In [24]:
#applying squareroot function to reduce skewness 
p=[]
for i in x.columns:
    b=np.sqrt(x[i])
    X1=pd.DataFrame(b)
    X2=X1.transpose()
    p.append(np.array([b]))
X=pd.DataFrame(np.concatenate(p))

X=X.transpose()
X.columns=x.columns
